data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in a quiet neighborhood in the highly sought after town of Meredith. This is single level living at its best with many updates done through out. The property also boasts a 2 car garage, large private fenced in back yard and screened in gazebo.  Turn key and ready for its new owners. Located just a short walk to downtown and Meredith Bay where you can enjoy great restaurants and Lake Winnepesaukee. This is a great Airbnb/rental opportunity!!!!   Call or Email for showings, by appointment only.
